  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety and efficacy of Immune Globulin Intravenous
      (Human), 10% (IGIV 10%) in subjects with primary immunodeficiency disorders.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
